{"tid":390650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新聞整合]挑! 原來天文台真係預撚錯晒降雨量同厄爾尼諾","createTime":"2017-09-07T08:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T10:02:16.000Z","uid":75358,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"626afa87b92c787bac6aabf24776435b175701ac","tid":390650,"uid":75358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"6月頭條日報: 「厄爾尼諾」現象影響 港<span style=\"color: red;\">今夏雨少</span>氣溫高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLink:<a href=\"http://news.stheadline.com/dailynews/content_hk/2017/06/02/410558.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.stheadline.com%2Fdailynews%2Fcontent_hk%2F2017%2F06%2F02%2F410558.asp&d=tkmTD006pdmnVmn%2Fno3as26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=bd2ec58b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.stheadline.com%2Fdailynews%2Fcontent_hk%2F2017%2F06%2F02%2F410558.asp&h=cd369eb0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.stheadline.com/dailynews/content_hk/2017/06/02/410558.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n7月蘋果日報追問: 豪雨7月！雨量16年來最多 今夏預測爆標？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLink:<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57025448&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170801\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57025448%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170801&d=tkmTD006pdmnVmn%2Fno3as26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=64ced49d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57025448%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170801&h=11ce4121\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57025448&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170801</a><br />\n上月的豪雨，亦推高今個夏季首兩個月的雨量，升至1,226毫米，多於正常47%。天文台早前預測，今年夏季雨量「正常至偏少」，即少於1,509毫米，<span style=\"color: red;\">惟今年6至7月已錄得1,226毫米，若8月降雨多於283毫米，便超出預測範圍。由於本港過往8月的雨量，平均有432毫米，若今個月的雨量正常至偏多，則有機會「爆標」。</span><br />\n<br />\n岑富祥回應指，天文台參考香港過去30多年的8月雨量數據，認為今年夏季的總雨量，「仍有一定機會在正常範圍之內（少於1,509毫米）」，現時無計劃調高夏季雨量預測。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(天文台仍然堅信無錯 結果8月降雨量489.1毫米，較同期升56.9毫米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b4frtoz8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb4frtoz8&h=3b320019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n9月6日蘋果再追問加BIN C: 今年仲會打多3次風？天文台調高逼港風暴數目預測<br />\nLink:<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170906/57172431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170906%2F57172431&d=tkmTD006pdmnVmn%2Fno3as26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=fcd9161c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170906%2F57172431&h=5df09bf4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170906/57172431</a><br />\n被問到為何天文台在年初「估細數」，天文台科學主任李鳳瑩回覆《蘋果》查詢時解釋，電腦氣候模式在年初預測厄爾尼諾的發展，<span style=\"color: red;\">與實況有些距離。</span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除風暴逼港數目被低估，<span style=\"color: red;\">雨量預測亦然。截至上月底，尖沙嘴天文台總部今年已錄得2,249毫米雨量，較正常多18%，</span>加上最新電腦預報顯示，香港今年餘下時間，雨量可能正常至偏少，天文台遂調高全年雨量預測，由原先預計的「正常至偏少」（少於2,650毫米），改為「正常至偏多」（多於2,150毫米）。<br />\n李鳳瑩解釋，世界各地的電腦氣候模式，年初預測華南在春夏季的降雨時，並無明確趨勢，令年初的雨量預測，與實況有相距。"},{"pid":"3c9b5cdcd909d48606fa8878d5604b04b39fd51a","tid":390650,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"氣溫高中一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2ff56f1980a3159ea2603a972ed3b7ad383935","tid":390650,"uid":75358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:46:23.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77331bbb63b217986eb5a51a454ecfef3a4b33b6","tid":390650,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:53:58.000Z","msg":"香港大交合對馬交氣象局真係海軍鬥水兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣個氣象局都好過你百倍 莫講話日本"},{"pid":"fcc34b76179bb9ebc76fe7da459c91affa6bce69","tid":390650,"uid":75358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"天文台遂調高全年雨量預測，由原先預計的「正常至偏少」（少於2,650毫米），改為「正常至偏多」（多於2,150毫米）。<br />\n<br />\n大交合淆到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原本預有上限 呢家改有下限無上限"},{"pid":"4b246147a05f30785a0d627c23ba1ecddfce260f","tid":390650,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}